    public interface UiWidgetSingleMutableComposite<CHILD extends UiWidget>
extends UiWidgetSingleComposite<CHILD>
    This is the abstract interface for a single composite widget that allows to set or replace its child.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
